1. `git checkout 5699f028 -- src/ include/ python/ tests/ tools/bench_tau_xi.sh` (7 个文件)
2. 保留 `examples/sdma/cu_xgmi_bench.cpp`, `tools/bench_xgmi_sdma_bw.sh`, `.cursor/rules/` (micro-bench infra + rule)
